
 - Will remain compatible with vtun-ng while still preserving autoconf and C

 - Will implement hardening features setuid and dropcaps for selected platforms

 - Will implement as much as possible the same requires and accept_encrypt client
   security configuration features as vtun-ng.

---

Comments, suggestion, wishes and if possible patches are always welcome.
Create an issue on github or send an email to sigsegv@radiotube.org.

Jan-Espen Oversand <sigsegv@radiotube.org>

